description: It's more than just snowcones; it's the Kona Ice Experience! It's the tropical environment we create with our Kona Entertainment Vehicle. From the fun calypso music, colorful truck, the do-it-yourself Flavorwave, and the always friendly and smiling staff - Everyone loves the Kona Ice Experience. We currently service the areas of Grand Prairie, Irving and Cedar Hill area.
name: Kona Ice North Grand Prairie
